+---
+title: "Cradling on the Move"
+summary: "Build ball control while running: the foundation of all lacrosse. 10 minutes."
+sport: "lacrosse-girls"
+ages: ["8-10"]
+focus: "fundamentals"
+layer: "foundations"
+fundamental: "cradling"
